    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Chaotic local multiplayer</h2>Throw your friends in the lava and be the last survivor when the rescue finally comes. <br>Fast and intuitive gameplay, up to 6 players on the same screen.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794670/extras/7cca241ba944b60c291cdc0eee531bd6.poster.avif?t=1675529833\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794670/extras/7cca241ba944b60c291cdc0eee531bd6.webm?t=1675529833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794670/extras/7cca241ba944b60c291cdc0eee531bd6.mp4?t=1675529833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use different spells to be successful</h2>Choose and cast devastating spells. <br><strong>More than 10 different spells already available !</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794670/extras/spells.PNG?t=1675529833\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Super fast learning</h2>All you need is an analog stick and 4 buttons to turn your friends in smoking roasts. Limited Rescue is very intuitive but it takes practise to truly master the elements !<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Free for all or in teams</h2>Limited Rescue already offers 3 different game modes so that you can bbq your friends alone or in teams.<br><br><br>The game can be played with a keyboard but we highly recommend the use of gamepads (xbox, PS4, ...) to better enjoy the experience.<br>Limited Rescue is &quot;Remote Play&quot; compatible --&gt; Only one of you needs to buy the game and is then able to invite the whole squad to join through Steam, even remotely.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1794670/extras/personnages.PNG?t=1675529833\" /></span>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语<strong>*</strong><br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
